snippet.title: Ore no Imouto Maker EX - Prologue [English Closed Captions]
snippet.description:
[ Game : 俺の妹めいかぁEX いもうとと恋しよ♪ぽ～たぶる (Ore no Imouto Maker EX - Imouto to Koi Shiyo Portable) ] [ Player : Ziddy ] [ Platform : PSP ] [ Language : Chinese (English Subtitles by jaypee) (TLCed by dango) (QCed by sm2345) ]

- Actual game starts at 0:30

- This game was released as a bonus disc for the original Oreimo PSP. The auto mode works slightly different from the original psp game, but hopefully you guys can read the text before it flies by.

- This game is considerably shorter than the main oreimo psp series, but we won't be focusing much of our attention on this, I just decided to release this since I had the video recorded in November last year.

- Go ahead and vote on which "sister" you want to see first. I have Kirino and Kuroneko events recorded already, if it might influence your decision.
